  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2b9283b6054aa4443b51ec1cd5098042, type: 3}
  m_Name: QuestionChoice7
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestionChoiceData
  Question: The Wolf begins to whimper, looking at his paws. "My paws are hurt from
    the 'noise.' I need you to come inside my dark den and help me fix them right
    now. No one else can help me but you."
  option1: I'm sorry you're hurting, but I can't go into your den. I will go find
    the Starry Merchant to bring you some medicine.
  option2: "Oh no! I\u2019ll come inside and help. I\u2019m a Celestial Weaver, so
    it\u2019s my job to fix things."
  option3: I'll come in for just one minute, but then I have to go back to my Garden.
